    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2017-11-07</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2018-06-11T21:37:16Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Indexing Narcotics, Fentanyl, and Opioids Act of 2017 or the INFO Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Secretary of Health and Human Services&nbsp;to appoint a federal coordinator&nbsp;within the Department of Health and Human Services to:</p> <ul> <li>coordinate&nbsp;programs related to opioid abuse reduction,</li> <li>liaise with state and local entities carrying out activities relating to opioid abuse reduction, and </li> <li>establish and operate a publicly available electronic database&nbsp;to facilitate&nbsp;data collection&nbsp;related to&nbsp;opioid abuse<strike></strike>.</li></ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
